er mile driven. Insurance here is also expensive, coming in at around $37. Although it would be practically impossible to do a 3,000 mile move over the course of ten days on the island, we still looked at the estimated cost for doing so through for the purpose of comparing the company to other truck rental services. The total cost for this long-trip would be $2580, the most expensive of all companies we looked at.","Their expensive price could be forgiven if they iffered the only truck rental services on the island, but U-Haul has a number of locations in the area, making it seem silly to pay more for a service that has fewer options. If you don’t like U-Haul for any given reason, then they may be your only option, but you should realize the price increase may be enough to ignore your issues with U-Haul.","The most disappointing feature of Harper though is the fact that they do not offer a guarantee or roadside assistance, which means that if something happens, they may come and fix it for you, or you might have to take the truck in yourself.","The only real factor that plays in their favor is the fact that they are one of only three companies that offer pick up services, but even then, the service seems limited to airport pick ups, which is likely to be unhelpful to many people in the moving process."]},"id":"44a1d65b-4f36-477f-9ae0-52d7eb08dcae","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"76034bb6-ffea-44ad-85f8-b791574a96b7","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["With expensive rental rates, poor customer service, minimal territory and limited service options, Harper Car and Truck Rentals is likely to be a last-choice for those who happen to be in their operating area."]},"id":"53d00912-bd8b-4a82-b6ad-8ef35053669b","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_50319","url":"/harper-car-and-truck-rental-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"billy-bommer","url":"/author/billy-bommer","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Billy Bommer",